SAVE THIS SKIN HACK 🧖🏻‍♀️🍵

Me & my girl tried this viral green tea face soak and we’re shook 😱💚
It’s giving spa day at home and our skin has never felt this fresh and smooth ✨
Perfect for tiny bumps, open pores, and that dull look you just wanna say bye to 🚫

What you need:👇🏻
• 1 green tea bag or loose green tea
• 1 cup hot water
• Cotton pads

How we used it:

1. Brew the green tea, let it cool
2. Soak cotton pads, apply on cheeks and t-zone
3. Chill for 15 mins, rinse off and glow 🧊

Why we love it: 😱
Green tea is packed with antioxidants, calms irritated skin, minimizes pores, and gives an instant refreshed glow. And the best part? It’s super affordable and all-natural 🌱

Try this with your skincare bestie & tag us if you do.

This isn’t just a drink, it’s a skin glow recipe disguised as a summer cooler 🧊✨

Fav combo: 
Sattu – 2 tbsp
Jaljeera powder 1tsp
Black salt – half tsp
Cumin powder – half tsp
Chaat masala – 1tsp
Lemon juice – half a lemon
Chopped mint leaves – 1 tbsp
Water – 1.5 cups (ice cubes optional) 🥤

Tastes earthy, feels refreshing, and does wonders for your skin. From flushing out toxins to keeping those surprise pimples away, this desi drink is a skincare savior in disguise.

Keeps you cool, keeps your glow cooler 😎💁🏻‍♀️
Try this before buying another expensive detox—your skin (and wallet) will thank you!!!!
